This script will:

- Set up Squid
- Check if all files needed to set up Squid are available
- Add the group squid
- Add the user squid
- Add the group squidadm
- Patch Squid
- Make and install Squid
- Install script for rotation of logs
- Install squid init script

You must download the source archive (tar.gz) file from http://www.squid-cache.org/Download/ and extract it to your desired directory. Then edit the line:

$ SQUID_SRCVER="2.6.STABLE18"
